{"tid":2416680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"迪士尼樂園有大陸婆上台打人  狂罵演員是豬","createTime":"2021-02-21T08:57:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T00:50:48.000Z","uid":184679,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"39c5c7bdd5e75342914b54f2de82a3b15240aa52","tid":2416680,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T08:57:04.000Z","msg":"近日內地流傳一段影片，一名女子在上海迪士尼劇場內，突然走上台打演員，打完後還狂罵：你這個豬，不配當中國人！<br />\n<br />\n片中見當時台上有數名演員正在表演，突然一名穿長裙戴帽及戴有口罩的女子，走上台追打其中一名演員，打完後還狂罵：你這個豬，不配當中國人！其他演員都被她的舉動嚇至呆立當場。<br />\n<br />\n隨後，現場工作人員勸該女子離場，但該女子卻執意不願離開，最終導致演出要取消。<br />\n<br />\n有現場觀眾指，演出前在大廳裡有段表演，因搞笑目的和劇情需要，出現了脫褲和抽鞭的場景。該女子認為以上2個行為影響了她女兒的正確價值觀，從而引發上台打人一幕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/hd/8453a8f6db7e0661fffaa0a315dbdea7/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210221/_2021022116394495283.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2F8453a8f6db7e0661fffaa0a315dbdea7%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210221%2F_2021022116394495283.jpg&h=4a02ed4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hd.stheadline. com/news/realtime/chi/2003910</code></pre>"},{"pid":"8d20ebc37d72b13fe7846e0460cde2f466cff204","tid":2416680,"uid":13303,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T08:58:34.000Z","msg":"符合蟈情<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3435ab71b6617798ad1fda090ea1c7184eb4178d","tid":2416680,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T09:11:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0738a64b2a847cbe770a5c2ac5610a0c37735d42","tid":2416680,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T09:16:47.000Z","msg":"福建一动物园白马遭人拳打